00:47:54,609 --> 00:47:56,611
IS THAT WHAT YOU WANT?

498
00:47:58,112 --> 00:48:02,116
[MEEK VOICE]
OH, NO.

499
00:48:02,116 --> 00:48:04,118
I'M STILL GRATEFUL FOR LOVE.

500
00:48:07,121 --> 00:48:09,624
[FIRM VOICE]
WHAT DO YOU WANT, THEN?

501
00:48:14,629 --> 00:48:18,633
[MEEK VOICE]
I PRAY FOR JAN TO COME HOME.

502
00:48:21,135 --> 00:48:24,138
[FIRM VOICE]
HE WILL BE COMING HOME
IN 10 DAYS.

503
00:48:24,138 --> 00:48:27,141
YOU MUST LEARN TO ENDURE.
YOU KNOW THAT.

504
00:48:32,146 --> 00:48:34,649
[MEEK VOICE]
OH, I CAN'T WAIT.

505
00:48:40,154 --> 00:48:42,657
[FIRM VOICE]
THIS IS UNLIKE YOU, BESS.

506
00:48:42,657 --> 00:48:47,161
OUT THERE, THERE ARE PEOPLE
WHO NEED JAN AND HIS WORK.

507
00:48:47,161 --> 00:48:49,163
WHAT ABOUT THEM?

508
00:48:53,167 --> 00:48:58,673
[MEEK VOICE]
THEY DON'T MATTER.
NOTHING ELSE MATTERS.

509
00:48:58,673 --> 00:49:02,677
I JUST WANT JAN HOME AGAIN.

510
00:49:03,177 --> 00:49:05,680
I PRAY TO YOU.

511
00:49:05,680 --> 00:49:09,684
OH, PLEASE,
WON'T YOU SEND HIM HOME?

512
00:49:14,188 --> 00:49:18,192
[FIRM VOICE]
ARE YOU SURE
THAT'S WHAT YOU WANT?

513
00:49:22,697 --> 00:49:25,199
[MEEK VOICE]
YES.

514
00:49:50,391 --> 00:49:52,393
OK. GET HER UP.

515
00:50:02,903 --> 00:50:04,905
BLOW OUT!

516
00:50:04,905 --> 00:50:05,906
[ALARM BEEPING]

517
00:50:05,906 --> 00:50:07,908
GET AWAY!
BLOW OUT!

518
00:50:07,908 --> 00:50:09,410
TERRY!

519
00:50:09,410 --> 00:50:10,411
TERRY!

520
00:50:19,036 --> 00:50:20,538
TERRY! TERRY!

521
00:50:23,924 --> 00:50:24,925
TERRY!

522
00:50:31,299 --> 00:50:32,933
TALK TO ME, WILL YOU?

523
00:50:38,806 --> 00:50:40,808
[MAN YELLING]

524
00:50:51,319 --> 00:50:52,320
WATCH OUT!

525
00:50:53,954 --> 00:50:55,956
JAN!

526
00:50:55,956 --> 00:50:59,460
GO GET--GET A MEDIC!

527
00:51:18,346 --> 00:51:21,349
Minister: I DON'T KNOW
WHAT KIND OF CONDITION
HE'S IN.

528
00:51:21,349 --> 00:51:24,735
I THINK IT'S
VERY SERIOUS, THOUGH.

529
00:51:24,735 --> 00:51:26,737
I DON'T QUITE KNOW.

530
00:51:33,744 --> 00:51:37,248
IT'S JAN. THERE'S BEEN
AN ACCIDENT ON THE RIG.

531
00:52:27,915 --> 00:52:29,917
[HELICOPTER ENGINE
RUMBLING]

532
00:52:32,420 --> 00:52:34,922
JAN, CAN YOU HEAR ME?

533
00:52:39,427 --> 00:52:41,429
OH.

534
00:52:49,687 --> 00:52:51,689
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

535
00:52:51,689 --> 00:52:54,191
I'M HOLDING
YOUR HAND.

536
00:52:54,191 --> 00:52:55,693
DON'T TOUCH ME.

537
00:52:55,693 --> 00:52:57,194
DON'T TOUCH ME!

538
00:52:57,194 --> 00:52:58,696
Man: JAN, RELAX.
JUST TAKE...

539
00:53:11,959 --> 00:53:13,461
SIT DOWN HERE.

540
00:53:17,965 --> 00:53:20,468
ALL RIGHT.
ALL RIGHT.

541
00:53:20,468 --> 00:53:22,970
SHH.
DEEP BREATH.

542
00:53:22,970 --> 00:53:25,473
HELLO. TALK
TO ME, DARLING.

543
00:53:25,473 --> 00:53:27,475
TALK TO ME.

544
00:53:27,475 --> 00:53:28,976
TALK TO ME.

545
00:53:29,477 --> 00:53:30,978
COME ON.
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

546
00:53:33,481 --> 00:53:35,483
IT'S ALL RIGHT.
IT'S GOING TO BE
ALL RIGHT.

547
00:53:53,634 --> 00:53:55,636
UH, THEY'RE GOING
TO OPERATE STRAIGHTAWAY.

548
00:53:55,636 --> 00:53:58,138
IT WILL BE
A FEW HOURS,

549
00:53:58,639 --> 00:53:59,640
SO I THINK
WE BETTER WAIT...

550
00:53:59,640 --> 00:54:01,642
Dodo: BESS.

551
00:54:01,642 --> 00:54:04,645
BESS, YOU CAN'T
GO IN THERE.

552
00:54:04,645 --> 00:54:06,146
IT'S
NOT ALLOWED.
I WANT TO BE WITH HIM.

553
00:54:06,146 --> 00:54:07,147
I KNOW YOU DO.
I KNOW.

554
00:54:07,147 --> 00:54:08,148
BUT COME ON.
COME WITH ME.
COME ON.

555
00:54:08,148 --> 00:54:10,651
NO. I WANT TO SEE HIM
ALL THE TIME.

556
00:54:10,651 --> 00:54:13,654
BESS, IT'S NOT
A GOOD IDEA.
COME ON.

557
00:54:13,654 --> 00:54:16,657
BESS. BESS, PLEASE,
YOU CAN'T STAY HERE.

558
00:54:17,157 --> 00:54:18,659
IT'S JUST NOT POSSIBLE.

559
00:54:18,659 --> 00:54:19,660
BESS!

560
00:54:19,660 --> 00:54:21,662
CAN I HAVE
A WORD WITH YOU?

561
00:54:21,662 --> 00:54:25,165
STAY THERE,
ALL RIGHT?
DON'T MOVE.

562
00:54:47,555 --> 00:54:50,558
I WANT YOU
TO PRAY WITH ME.

563
00:54:53,561 --> 00:54:54,061
Dodo: BUT...

564
00:54:54,562 --> 00:54:56,063
PLEASE.

565
00:55:10,711 --> 00:55:15,215
DEAR GOD,
WE PRAY THAT YOU

566
00:55:15,716 --> 00:55:18,719
WILL HOLD YOUR HAND
OVER JAN

567
00:55:19,219 --> 00:55:22,723
AND NOT LET HIM DIE.

568
00:55:22,723 --> 00:55:24,224
[TOGETHER]
AMEN.

569
00:55:59,510 --> 00:56:03,013
MRS. NYMAN,
WILL YOU PLEASE
COME WITH ME?

570
00:56:32,543 --> 00:56:35,045
WILL HE LIVE?

571
00:56:35,045 --> 00:56:42,052
WE HAVE STABILIZED
YOUR HUSBAND'S CONDITION
FOR THE TIME BEING.

572
00:56:45,055 --> 00:56:47,558
WILL HE LIVE?

573
00:56:47,558 --> 00:56:50,561
YES. YES, BESS,
HE WILL LIVE.

574
00:56:58,569 --> 00:57:02,072
YOUR HUSBAND SUFFERED
VERY SERIOUS INJURIES.

575
00:57:04,074 --> 00:57:07,578
LIFE SHOULDN'T ALWAYS
BE PRESERVED AT ANY COST.

576
00:57:09,830 --> 00:57:11,832
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

577
00:57:14,835 --> 00:57:17,337
UM, WELL, THE DOCTOR
MEANS, BESS,

578
00:57:17,337 --> 00:57:21,341
THAT, UM, SOMETIMES...

579
00:57:21,842 --> 00:57:24,845
IN SOME CASES
WHEN LIFE ISN'T
WORTH LIVING,

580
00:57:24,845 --> 00:57:28,348
THEN IT MAY
BE BETTER TO DIE.

581
00:57:33,353 --> 00:57:39,359
YOU DON'T KNOW JAN,
OR YOU COULD NOT
SAY SUCH A THING.

582
00:57:40,861 --> 00:57:44,364
YOUR HUSBAND
MAY NEVER WALK AGAIN.

583
00:57:44,364 --> 00:57:47,868
WE THINK HE'LL BE
COMPLETELY PARALYZED.

584
00:57:49,870 --> 00:57:51,872
BUT HE'LL LIVE?

585
00:57:51,872 --> 00:57:55,876
YES. HE WILL LIVE,
IT SEEMS.

586
00:58:05,502 --> 00:58:07,137
[MEEK VOICE]
FATHER.

587
00:58:08,639 --> 00:58:11,141
ARE YOU THERE?

588
00:58:11,141 --> 00:58:13,143
ARE YOU STILL THERE?

589
00:58:17,648 --> 00:58:20,150
[FIRM VOICE]
OF COURSE I AM, BESS.

590
00:58:20,150 --> 00:58:21,652
YOU KNOW THAT.

591
00:58:31,161 --> 00:58:33,664
[MEEK VOICE]
WHAT'S HAPPENING?

592
00:58:39,169 --> 00:58:42,673
[FIRM VOICE]
YOU WANTED JAN HOME.

593
00:58:46,176 --> 00:58:48,679
[MEEK VOICE]
I'VE CHANGED MY MIND.

594
00:58:48,679 --> 00:58:50,681
WHY DID I ASK
FOR THAT?

595
00:58:53,684 --> 00:58:55,185
[FIRM VOICE]
BECAUSE YOU'RE

596
00:58:55,686 --> 00:58:58,188
A STUPID
LITTLE GIRL, BESS.

597
00:58:58,188 --> 00:59:01,191
I HAD TO TEST YOU.

598
00:59:01,191 --> 00:59:05,195
YOUR LOVE FOR JAN
HAS BEEN PUT TO THE TEST.

599
00:59:13,704 --> 00:59:15,205
[MEEK VOICE]
THANK YOU

600
00:59:15,205 --> 00:59:17,207
FOR NOT LETTING HIM DIE.

601
00:59:22,212 --> 00:59:24,214
[FIRM VOICE]
YOU'RE WELCOME, BESS.

602
00:59:39,847 --> 00:59:45,853
?? HE SAID
  "THERE IS NO REASON ??

603
00:59:45,853 --> 00:59:48,856
?? AND THE TRUTH
IS PLAIN TO SEE" ??

604
00:59:51,859 --> 00:59:55,863
?? BUT I WANDERED
THROUGH MY PLAYING CARDS ??

605
00:59:58,365 --> 01:00:01,869
?? AND WOULD NOT
LET HER BE ??

606
01:00:04,872 --> 01:00:08,876
?? ONE OF 16
VESTAL VIRGINS ??

607
01:00:11,378 --> 01:00:14,381
?? WHO WERE LEAVING
FOR THE COAST ??

608
01:00:17,885 --> 01:00:22,389
?? AND ALTHOUGH
MY EYES WERE OPEN ??

609
01:00:24,391 --> 01:00:27,895
?? THEY MIGHT JUST AS WELL
HAVE BEEN CLOSED ??

610
01:00:27,895 --> 01:00:30,397
?? AND SO IT WAS... ??

611
01:00:30,397 --> 01:00:34,401
Minister: I WOULD SAY TO YOU...

612
01:00:34,401 --> 01:00:37,905
THAT IF THERE IS
ONE OF THESE COMMANDMENTS

613
01:00:37,905 --> 01:00:43,410
WHICH YOU DO NOT LOVE
AND DO NOT OBEY,

614
01:00:43,410 --> 01:00:47,414
YOU HAVE NO PLACE
AT THE LORD'S TABLE.

615
01:00:47,414 --> 01:00:49,533
[SINGING HYMN]

616
01:01:12,055 --> 01:01:13,557
WHEN DID YOU
GET BACK?

617
01:01:13,557 --> 01:01:15,058
I CAME BACK
WITH JAN.

618
01:01:15,559 --> 01:01:17,561
OH, IT'S GOOD
TO SEE YOU.

619
01:01:32,876 --> 01:01:34,378
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

620
01:01:34,378 --> 01:01:37,247
OH, SURF'S UP!

621
01:01:37,247 --> 01:01:38,382
Pits: HI.

622
01:01:38,382 --> 01:01:39,383
Jan: HI, GUYS.

623
01:01:39,883 --> 01:01:40,884
Terry: HOW YOU DOING,
BUDDY?

624
01:01:40,884 --> 01:01:42,886
WELL, FINE.
HOW ARE YOU?

625
01:01:42,886 --> 01:01:44,388
OK.

626
01:01:47,391 --> 01:01:48,892
DID YOU FIND ANYTHING?

627
01:01:49,393 --> 01:01:50,894
Terry: GAS.

628
01:01:50,894 --> 01:01:52,396
NOTHING REALLY.

629
01:01:52,396 --> 01:01:54,398
HA HA!
GUESS WHAT, NOW.

630
01:01:54,398 --> 01:01:55,899
WE'RE HEADING UP NORTH.

631
01:01:55,899 --> 01:01:57,401
WELL, NORTH,
THAT'S GOOD.

632
01:01:57,901 --> 01:02:00,404
THAT'S WHERE YOU
ALWAYS SAID THE OIL WAS.

633
01:02:00,771 --> 01:02:02,773
WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE, ANYWAY?

634
01:02:02,773 --> 01:02:04,775
WE'RE MEANT TO BE
OUT DRILLING.

635
01:02:04,775 --> 01:02:06,276
[OPENS CAN]

636
01:02:06,276 --> 01:02:07,778
Jan:
I JUST FELT LIKE

637
01:02:07,778 --> 01:02:10,280
PUTTING MY FEET UP
FOR A WHILE.

638
01:02:10,414 --> 01:02:13,917
I DIDN'T TRUST
YOU 2 GUYS
OUT THERE ALONE.

639
01:02:13,917 --> 01:02:15,919
[LAUGHTER]

640
01:02:15,919 --> 01:02:17,921
[CANS OPENING]

641
01:02:25,679 --> 01:02:27,681
OH, MY...

642
01:02:27,681 --> 01:02:30,684
MY ARMS AREN'T OK, SO...

643
01:02:30,684 --> 01:02:33,186
I'M NOT THIRSTY, ANYWAY.

644
01:02:35,188 --> 01:02:38,191
BULLSHIT!

645
01:02:42,312 --> 01:02:44,314
HEY, COME ON.

646
01:02:44,314 --> 01:02:45,816
COME ON.

647
01:02:48,318 --> 01:02:50,320
OH, MAN, SORRY.

648
01:02:54,825 --> 01:02:56,827
[COUGHING]

649
01:02:56,827 --> 01:02:58,328
OH, MAN, SORRY.

650
01:02:58,829 --> 01:03:00,330
OK.

651
01:03:00,330 --> 01:03:02,332
THANK YOU.

652
01:03:13,093 --> 01:03:17,097
I'M NOT REALLY
SUPPOSED TO HAVE
ANY VISITORS, SO...

653
01:03:17,097 --> 01:03:19,599
Terry: WE REALLY DON'T HAVE
THE TIME, EITHER.

654
01:03:19,599 --> 01:03:21,601
HA HA HA! OK.

655
01:03:21,601 --> 01:03:23,603
YOU TAKE CARE
OF YOURSELF, HUH?

656
01:03:24,104 --> 01:03:26,606
Pits: TAKE CARE.
GET WELL SOON.

657
01:03:26,606 --> 01:03:28,108
SEE YOU, GUYS.

658
01:03:28,608 --> 01:03:29,609
[DOOR OPENS]

659
01:03:30,110 --> 01:03:31,611
[DOOR CLOSES]

660
01:03:39,619 --> 01:03:42,122
WILL YOU DO
SOMETHING FOR ME?

661
01:03:42,122 --> 01:03:43,623
YES.

662
01:03:46,126 --> 01:03:48,128
THE NEXT TIME YOU COME,

663
01:03:48,128 --> 01:03:49,629
COULD YOU WEAR
SOMETHING MORE...

664
01:03:51,631 --> 01:03:53,633
MORE LOOSE...

665
01:03:56,136 --> 01:03:58,638
SO I, UH...

666
01:03:58,638 --> 01:04:01,141
SO I WON'T HAVE TO SEE
YOUR BODY.

667
01:04:23,413 --> 01:04:25,415
[SOBBING]

668
01:04:31,922 --> 01:04:33,924
[DOOR OPENS]

669
01:04:39,679 --> 01:04:42,682
BESS, YOU'LL
HAVE TO GO NOW

670
01:04:42,682 --> 01:04:44,684
BECAUSE JAN NEEDS
TO REST.

671
01:04:45,185 --> 01:04:46,686
ALL RIGHT.

672
01:04:54,694 --> 01:04:56,696
[DOOR CLOSES]

673
01:04:58,949 --> 01:05:01,451
YOU SHOULDN'T GET HIM
TOO OVEREMOTIONAL,
YOU KNOW.

674
01:05:01,451 --> 01:05:03,453
IT'S NOT GOOD FOR HIM.

675
01:05:03,453 --> 01:05:05,956
I'M SORRY.

676
01:05:05,956 --> 01:05:08,458
YOU GOT TO
CHEER HIM UP.

677
01:05:11,962 --> 01:05:13,964
IS HE ASLEEP NOW?

678
01:05:13,964 --> 01:05:15,966
WELL, HE SHOULD BE...

679
01:05:16,466 --> 01:05:18,468
THE AMOUNT
I'VE GIVEN HIM.

680
01:05:20,103 --> 01:05:21,605
WOULD IT BE
ALL RIGHT

681
01:05:21,605 --> 01:05:24,608
IF I WENT AND HAD
A LOOK AT HIM?

682
01:05:44,628 --> 01:05:47,130
I LOVE YOU, JAN.

683
01:05:55,639 --> 01:05:59,643
[IMITATING JAN]
I LOVE YOU,
TOO, BESS.

684
01:05:59,643 --> 01:06:03,146
YOU ARE THE LOVE
OF MY LIFE.

685
01:06:23,700 --> 01:06:25,702
BESS.

686
01:06:28,705 --> 01:06:30,707
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?

687
01:06:30,707 --> 01:06:33,209
I'VE BEEN
TO THE CHURCH.

688
01:06:36,212 --> 01:06:38,715
WHAT, AT 2:00
IN THE MORNING?

689
01:06:44,721 --> 01:06:47,223
I DON'T WANT YOU
GETTING ILL AGAIN...

690
01:06:47,724 --> 01:06:49,225
LIKE YOU DID
WHEN SAM DIED.

691
01:06:49,225 --> 01:06:51,227
I SAID I'VE BEEN
TO THE CHURCH.

692
01:06:51,227 --> 01:06:53,229
IT HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH THE CHURCH.

693
01:06:53,730 --> 01:06:56,733
DID YOU HEAR
WHAT I SAID? DID YOU?

694
01:06:58,234 --> 01:07:00,737
I DON'T WANT YOU
TO GET ILL AGAIN

695
01:07:00,737 --> 01:07:03,239
LIKE YOU DID
WHEN SAM DIED.

696
01:07:03,239 --> 01:07:06,743
I'VE HAD A WORD
WITH DR. RICHARDSON,
ALL RIGHT?

697
01:07:06,743 --> 01:07:09,746
AND HE SAYS
HE COULD SEE YOU TOMORROW.

698
01:07:09,746 --> 01:07:12,248
OH, CAN HE?

699
01:07:18,254 --> 01:07:19,756
[DOOR OPENS]

700
01:07:19,756 --> 01:07:22,759
BESS, WOULD YOU LIKE
TO COME IN?

701
01:07:36,272 --> 01:07:38,274
[DRAWER OPENS]

702
01:07:44,914 --> 01:07:47,417
DODO SAID
I HAD TO COME.

703
01:07:47,417 --> 01:07:51,287
SHE HAS THIS IDEA
ABOUT ME TREATING YOU.

704
01:07:54,290 --> 01:07:57,794
MY PREDECESSOR ADMITTED YOU
A FEW YEARS AGO.

705
01:07:58,795 --> 01:08:01,297
WELL, WHY DID HE
DO THAT?

706
01:08:01,798 --> 01:08:03,800
I DON'T KNOW.

707
01:08:03,800 --> 01:08:06,302
NO, NOR DO I.

708
01:08:06,302 --> 01:08:09,305
YOU WERE UPSET BECAUSE
YOUR BROTHER HAD DIED,

709
01:08:09,305 --> 01:08:13,059
AND NOW YOU'RE UPSET
BECAUSE YOUR HUSBAND'S ILL.

710
01:08:13,059 --> 01:08:15,061
NOTHING UNUSUAL
ABOUT THAT.

711
01:08:17,564 --> 01:08:20,567
AM I NOT GOING TO
HAVE SOME PILLS?

712
01:08:21,067 --> 01:08:23,069
I'M PROBABLY NOT LIKE
YOUR OLD DOCTOR.

713
01:08:23,069 --> 01:08:25,572
I DON'T THINK THAT PEOPLE
SHOULD BE GIVEN PILLS

714
01:08:25,572 --> 01:08:27,574
JUST BECAUSE THEY DO
WHAT'S ONLY NATURAL.

715
01:08:28,825 --> 01:08:31,828
MAYBE SHOWING WHAT YOU FEEL
ISN'T THE DONE THING

716
01:08:31,828 --> 01:08:33,329
FROM WHERE
YOU COME FROM,

717
01:08:33,329 --> 01:08:35,832
BUT IT'S CERTAINLY
NO DISEASE.

718
01:08:36,833 --> 01:08:39,836
WHAT...HAPPENED
ON THE RIG

719
01:08:39,836 --> 01:08:41,838
WAS MY FAULT.

720
01:08:43,339 --> 01:08:44,841
HOW COME?

721
01:08:46,843 --> 01:08:49,846
I PRAYED TO GOD
TO SEND HIM HOME.

722
01:08:52,348 --> 01:08:54,350
WELL...

723
01:08:57,854 --> 01:08:59,856
WELL...

724
01:08:59,856 --> 01:09:02,859
WHAT POWERS
YOU POSSESS.

725
01:09:02,859 --> 01:09:04,360
DO YOU REALLY...

726
01:09:04,861 --> 01:09:07,363
DO YOU REALLY BELIEVE
THAT YOU POSSESS
SUCH POWERS?

727
01:09:08,865 --> 01:09:12,752
I KNOW YOU PEOPLE BELIEVE
A LOT ABOUT YOURSELVES.

728
01:09:12,752 --> 01:09:14,254
BESS...

729
01:09:14,254 --> 01:09:16,756
PERHAPS YOU SHOULD DO
A BIT OF GRIEVING

730
01:09:16,756 --> 01:09:18,258
FOR YOURSELF
INSTEAD OF HIM.

731
01:09:18,758 --> 01:09:20,760
I THINK YOU SHOULD
COME AND SEE ME

732
01:09:20,760 --> 01:09:22,762
NOW AND AGAIN
IF YOU FEEL LIKE IT.

733
01:09:28,635 --> 01:09:30,637
I'M SORRY.

734
01:09:30,637 --> 01:09:32,138
OH. HA HA!

735
01:09:32,138 --> 01:09:33,640
COME ON.

736
01:09:35,642 --> 01:09:38,528
WELL, THINGS WILL PICK UP
ONCE HE GETS HOME AGAIN.

737
01:09:45,285 --> 01:09:47,287
??
T. Rex:
?? WELL, SHE'S MY WOMAN OF GOLD

738
01:09:47,287 --> 01:09:50,290
?? YES, SHE'S NOT VERY OLD,
