795
01:14:00,406 --> 01:14:02,041
[DOOR CLOSES]

796
01:14:21,060 --> 01:14:22,678
YOU MUST MAKE UP
WITH HIM.

797
01:14:23,179 --> 01:14:24,680
A HUSBAND AND WIFE

798
01:14:24,680 --> 01:14:27,683
HAVE TO BE ABLE
TO TALK TO EACH OTHER.

799
01:14:27,683 --> 01:14:30,186
HE'S THE ONE
WHO IS HELPLESS,

800
01:14:30,186 --> 01:14:31,687
AND YOU'RE THE ONE

801
01:14:32,188 --> 01:14:35,191
WHO MUST SHOW
YOU'RE STRONG.

802
01:14:35,191 --> 01:14:37,693
GO TO HIM AND TELL HIM

803
01:14:37,693 --> 01:14:40,696
YOU ARE SORRY
YOU WERE ANGRY.

804
01:14:40,696 --> 01:14:42,698
YOU HAVE GOD.

805
01:14:43,199 --> 01:14:44,700
YOU HAVE THE STRENGTH

806
01:14:44,700 --> 01:14:48,204
YOUR LIFE IN GOD
HAS BESTOWED UPON YOU,

807
01:14:48,204 --> 01:14:52,842
AND THAT IS A STRENGTH
HE DOES NOT POSSESS.

808
01:15:56,772 --> 01:15:58,774
OH, NO.

809
01:15:58,774 --> 01:16:01,277
COME ON.

810
01:16:01,277 --> 01:16:03,779
COME ON.
YOU'RE ALL RIGHT.

811
01:16:03,779 --> 01:16:05,665
COME ON. THAT'S IT.

812
01:16:06,165 --> 01:16:08,668
THAT'S IT.
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

813
01:16:08,668 --> 01:16:11,170
IT'S ALL RIGHT.
ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT.

814
01:16:14,040 --> 01:16:15,541
WHAT'S SHE THINKING OF,

815
01:16:15,541 --> 01:16:18,544
GOING OFF LEAVING
YOU LIKE THIS?

816
01:16:18,544 --> 01:16:21,047
YOU MUST ADMIT
THAT SHE WAS...

817
01:16:24,050 --> 01:16:27,053
SHE WAS HAPPY
WHEN WE GOT MARRIED.

818
01:16:31,440 --> 01:16:33,943
SHE BLOSSOMED...

819
01:16:33,943 --> 01:16:36,445
DIDN'T SHE?

820
01:16:42,818 --> 01:16:44,820
I CAN'T JUST
LIE HERE.

821
01:16:48,324 --> 01:16:51,827
I CAN'T EVEN
MAKE LOVE TO HER.

822
01:16:53,579 --> 01:16:55,581
SHE'S GOT TO
GET OUT OF HERE.

823
01:16:57,583 --> 01:17:00,586
SHE'S GOT TO GET ON
WITH LIFE.

824
01:17:01,087 --> 01:17:02,588
HELP ME
SET HER FREE.

825
01:17:09,478 --> 01:17:11,981
SHE'D DO ANYTHING
FOR YOU, JAN.

826
01:17:11,981 --> 01:17:13,983
YOU KNOW THAT.

827
01:17:13,983 --> 01:17:16,485
SHE DON'T CARE
ANYTHING ABOUT HERSELF...

828
01:17:18,487 --> 01:17:20,489
BUT SHE'D DO
ANYTHING FOR YOU...

829
01:17:21,991 --> 01:17:24,994
