ON YOUR FACE.

830
01:17:25,995 --> 01:17:27,496
DO YOU UNDERSTAND ME?

831
01:17:31,500 --> 01:17:33,002
YEAH.

832
01:17:33,002 --> 01:17:35,004
RIGHT.

833
01:17:37,006 --> 01:17:39,125
THANKS
FOR TELLING ME.

834
01:17:39,125 --> 01:17:40,626
NO TROUBLE.

835
01:17:43,629 --> 01:17:46,132
DO YOU WANT ME
TO READ TO YOU?

836
01:17:46,132 --> 01:17:48,134
HMM?

837
01:17:51,137 --> 01:17:52,638
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

838
01:18:37,600 --> 01:18:39,101
[FOOTSTEPS]

839
01:18:41,103 --> 01:18:43,606
