TO THE HOSPITAL.

840
01:18:46,993 --> 01:18:48,494
Dodo: BESS.

841
01:18:48,995 --> 01:18:49,996
BESS,
WHAT IS GOING ON?

842
01:18:49,996 --> 01:18:52,498
HE WENT UNCONSCIOUS.
WE HAD TO BRING HIM
BACK HERE.

843
01:18:52,498 --> 01:18:54,500
AT HOME ANYMORE--

844
01:18:54,500 --> 01:18:56,002
NOT IF YOU'RE
GOING TO GO
RUNNING OFF

845
01:18:56,502 --> 01:18:57,503
AND LEAVING HIM
LIKE THAT.

846
01:18:57,503 --> 01:18:59,005
I'M SORRY.

847
01:18:59,005 --> 01:19:01,007
WELL, IT'S JUST NOT
GOOD ENOUGH!

848
01:19:01,007 --> 01:19:03,509
I'M NOT--
I'M NOT EVEN ALLOWED
TO KISS HIM ANYMORE.

849
01:19:03,509 --> 01:19:07,013
WHY DON'T YOU TRY
LISTENING TO WHAT
HE SAYS, BESS?

850
01:19:07,013 --> 01:19:08,514
IT'S UP TO YOU.

851
01:19:09,015 --> 01:19:11,017
HE AIN'T GOT
ANYONE ELSE.

852
01:19:11,017 --> 01:19:13,019
YOU COULD GIVE HIM
THE WILL TO LIVE.

853
01:19:13,019 --> 01:19:15,521
THAT'S MORE THAN
ANY DOCTOR CAN DO.

854
01:19:30,036 --> 01:19:32,538
BESS?

855
01:19:32,655 --> 01:19:34,657
I'M SORRY.

856
01:19:37,043 --> 01:19:39,045
NO, IT WAS MY FAULT.

857
01:19:39,045 --> 01:19:40,546
COME HERE.

858
01:19:49,171 --> 01:19:50,673
HI.

859
01:19:50,923 --> 01:19:52,425
HI.

860
01:19:59,682 --> 01:20:02,184
LOVE IS
A MIGHTY POWER...

861
01:20:03,686 --> 01:20:05,187
ISN'T IT?

862
01:20:09,191 --> 01:20:11,193
IF I DIE...

863
01:20:11,193 --> 01:20:15,448
