TO TALK TO YOU
LIKE THAT AGAIN?

871
01:20:40,606 --> 01:20:41,607
I'D LOVE TO.

872
01:20:41,607 --> 01:20:43,109
BESS.

873
01:20:44,610 --> 01:20:49,115
